title: Beautifully Remodeled Home, Kitchen with Large Island, A/C, W/D
posting_body: ['Beautifully Remodeled Home, Kitchen with Large Island, A/C, W/D, Nice Yards!', 'Property Address', '148 W Maude Ave | Sunnyvale, CA 94085-4303', 'Offered By', 'Presidential Real Estate, Inc', 'Description', '148 W Maude Ave, Sunnyvale, CA  94085  (Maude/Stowell)', 'Spacious and remodeled single family home with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a 1 car garage.', ' The home was completely renovated in 2020 to include a new kitchen with island, vaulted ceilings, forced air heating and air conditioning, wood flooring, fresh paint, and dual pane windows.', ' The home is very spacious with has an open floor plan.', 'Separate laundry room with washer/dryer.', '  The back yard is very nice with a built in bbq and awning.', ' One year lease required.', ' Gardener included.', 'Cal DRE# 01998337', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 3BD/2.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,652', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $4,450.00', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $4,000.00']
